<ab facs="#facs_263_r1l7">Amergew / vnd von Amergew <expan>herwıd<ex>er</ex></expan> aws gen <expan>Augſp<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> / darein </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_263_r1l8">die <expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> Peytigö / den von Schöngö <expan>ſprech<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> gepeten / vns </ab>
